data.description: Rare opportunity to own a gorgeous, executive brick home in desirable Austins Landing!  This well maintained  6 bedroom home is ready to start entertaining your friends and family and enjoy.  Stunning covered front porch greets you as you enter the front door into a welcoming 2 story foyer leading into a sunny 2 story great room with floor to ceiling windows, stone fireplace and built in bookcases.  Large open floor plan includes a master bedroom AND guest suite/office with 2 full baths on main, large dining room, huge chef kitchen with breakfast area, all new upgraded stainless steel appliances, plenty of light, tons of cabinets and pantry storage that opens up to cozy family/keeping room with connecting fireplace. This home is full of upgrades including beautiful hardwoods, security system, upgraded moldings, coffered and vaulted ceilings, gorgeous staircases, spacious laundry room with sink, oversized garage, low HOA.   Upstairs has 3 large bedrooms and 2 full baths and so much closet space.  Newly finished walkout basement includes a bedroom, bathroom, media room, game room, workout area, flex room, panic room and plenty of storage.  Basement is even wired for a kitchen area and arcade area.  The private backyard includes an new expansive deck and new fence. Great schools and just minutes from Mall of GA, restaurants, entertainment, quick access to 85 & 316 and a short drive to downtown to Atlanta & UGA.
